<vm-player autoplay muted>
  <vm-video poster="/media/poster.png" cross-origin>

    <track
      default
      kind="subtitles"
      src="/media/subs/en.vtt"
      srclang="en"
      label="English"
    />
  </vm-video>


  <vm-default-ui />
</vm-player>
